name: Leonid laitskyi
details: The engineer Leonid Laitskyi is a assistant professior at the Institute of advanced Studies at the University of Melborne, and a research director at the RMST. He was awarded the nobel prize in Web devolopment in 2017 for his research on single page application for Facebook
